\/","url_meta":{"origin":279,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Vanity: Earth swallows man dragging his garment","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhile a man was trailing his robe out of vanity, he was suddenly swallowed up, and he will be buried in the earth until the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5790 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14869,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/earth-swallows-man-arrogance\/","url_meta":{"origin":279,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Vanity: Earth swallows a man impressed by himself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhile a man was walking in a fine garment, with his hair groomed and impressed with himself, Allah caused the earth to swallow him up. He will be buried until the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5789,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":810,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/25\/perfect-justice-day-resurrection\/","url_meta":{"origin":279,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Iqtisas: Perfect justice restored on Day of Resurrection","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 25, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe rights of justice will surely be restored to their people on the Day of Resurrection, even the hornless sheep will lay claim to the horned sheep.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2582 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":710,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/04\/18\/guard-yourself-greed-thulm\/","url_meta":{"origin":279,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Injustice: Guard yourself from oppression, greed, violence","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn 'Abdillah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBeware of committing\u00a0oppression, for oppression will be darkness on the Day of Resurrection. Beware of\u00a0greed, for greed ruined those before you. It caused them to shed their blood and to make lawful what was unlawful\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/279","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embedda